Invocation Name: pizza or wings
des:
Pizza or Wings is an entertaining way to determine your nights long dream of late night food. 

For college kids, as the nights get later the food options are longer and then you are left with the tough decision of Pizza or Wings.

Alexa will ask a few quick question to determine what needs to be ordered.
priv: The developer reported that this skill does not collect personal information.
